[
    {
        "content": "<p>From what I understand, a lot of work has been done to define sheaf cohomology <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=CategoryTheory.Sheaf.H#doc\">docs#CategoryTheory.Sheaf.H</a> on the category-theoretic side, and on the algebraic-geometric side we have <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.etaleTopology#doc\">docs#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.etaleTopology</a>. What then is the status of étale cohomology? (Apologies for the slightly open-ended question - I am relatively new to this area of mathlib.)</p>",
        "id": 535036842,
        "sender_full_name": "Bryan Wang",
        "timestamp": 1755561800
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>With the current mathlib, we can already define étale cohomology types for <code>X : Scheme.{u}</code>. Currently, these groups shall be in <code>Type (u + 2)</code>. With very little effort, we can make it into <code>Type (u + 1)</code>. With slightly more effort, it will eventually be defined in <code>Type u</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Sites.SheafCohomology.Basic</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.AlgebraicGeometry.Sites.Etale</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Algebra.Category.ModuleCat.AB</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Algebra.Category.Grp.ZModuleEquivalence</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Algebra.Homology.DerivedCategory.Ext.EnoughInjectives</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Abelian.GrothendieckCategory.EnoughInjectives</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Abelian.GrothendieckAxioms.Sheaf</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CategoryTheory</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Scheme</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">local</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HasExt</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HasExt.standard</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F.H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsGrothendieckAbelian</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleCat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleCat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ULift</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≌</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleCat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsGrothendieckAbelian.of_equivalence</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsGrothendieckAbelian</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">IsGrothendieckAbelian.of_equivalence</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">forget₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleCat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">asEquivalence</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsGrothendieckAbelian</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">where</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">local</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HasExt</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">hasExt_of_enoughInjectives</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F.H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- With additional work (e.g. #19462)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">})</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HasSheafify</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">local</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HasExt</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Sheaf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X.smallEtaleTopology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F.H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
